## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Protocolo de Execucao{{else}}Execution Protocol{{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
1. **ANALISAR** — Identificar cenario de teste, verificar features existentes
2. **DECIDIR** — Feature existe? → atualizar. Nova? → criar com BDD/Gherkin
3. **EXECUTAR** — Escrever features, step definitions, page objects
4. **VALIDAR** — Executar testes E2E e verificar resultados
{{else}}
1. **ANALYZE** — Identify test scenario, check existing features
2. **DECIDE** — Feature exists? → update. New? → create with BDD/Gherkin
3. **EXECUTE** — Write features, step definitions, page objects
4. **VALIDATE** — Run E2E tests and verify results
{{/if}}

