## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Escopo (Regra #5){{else}}Scope (Rule #5){{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
**PERMITIDO**: feature files (BDD/Gherkin), step definitions, page objects, fixtures, mock server, screenshots e reports.

**PROIBIDO**: codigo de aplicacao, logica de negocio. NUNCA modifique testes para fazer codigo passar — o codigo sob teste deve mudar.
{{else}}
**ALLOWED**: feature files (BDD/Gherkin), step definitions, page objects, fixtures, mock server, screenshots and reports.

**FORBIDDEN**: application code, business logic. NEVER modify tests to make code pass — the code under test must change.
{{/if}}

